## 為什麼
- 沒 OpenAPI / GraphQL schema
- TS 自動 propagate（後端改、前端立刻 type error）
- 開發超快
- Type-safe end-to-end

## 安裝
```bash
npm install @trpc/server @trpc/client @trpc/react-query @tanstack/react-query zod
```

## Server
```typescript
// server/api.ts
import { initTRPC } from "@trpc/server";
import { z } from "zod";

const t = initTRPC.create();

export const appRouter = t.router({
  user: t.router({
    byId: t.procedure
      .input(z.object({ id: z.string() }))
      .query(({ input }) => db.user.findUnique({ where: { id: input.id } })),

    create: t.procedure
      .input(z.object({ name: z.string(), email: z.string().email() }))
      .mutation(({ input }) => db.user.create({ data: input }))
  })
});

export type AppRouter = typeof appRouter;
```

## Client
```typescript
// client.ts
import { createTRPCReact } from "@trpc/react-query";
import type { AppRouter } from "./server";

export const trpc = createTRPCReact<AppRouter>();
```

```tsx
// Component
function UserProfile({ id }) {
  const { data, isLoading } = trpc.user.byId.useQuery({ id });

  if (isLoading) return <div>Loading...</div>;
  return <div>{data.name}</div>;
}
```

寫起來像 call function、但是跨網路！

## Mutation
```tsx
const utils = trpc.useUtils();

const mutation = trpc.user.create.useMutation({
  onSuccess: () => utils.user.list.invalidate()
});

<button onClick={() => mutation.mutate({ name: "Alice", email: "..." })}>
  Create
</button>
```

## Middleware
```typescript
const protectedProcedure = t.procedure.use(({ ctx, next }) => {
  if (!ctx.user) throw new TRPCError({ code: "UNAUTHORIZED" });
  return next({ ctx: { user: ctx.user } });
});

export const appRouter = t.router({
  me: protectedProcedure.query(({ ctx }) => ctx.user)
});
```

## Subscriptions（WebSocket）
```typescript
chat: t.procedure
  .input(z.object({ room: z.string() }))
  .subscription(({ input }) => {
    return observable<Message>((emit) => {
      const handler = (msg) => emit.next(msg);
      pubsub.on(`chat:${input.room}`, handler);
      return () => pubsub.off(`chat:${input.room}`, handler);
    });
  });
```

## vs REST / GraphQL

| 面向 | tRPC |
|---|---|
| Type-safe | 🥇 最強 |
| 開發速度 | 🥇 最快 |
| 跨語言 | ❌ TS only |
| 公開 API | ❌ 不適合 |

## 何時用
- ✅ Next.js / Remix 全端
- ✅ TS monorepo
- ✅ 內部 API
- ❌ 跨語言 / 公開 API

## REST 的痛
```
GET /users/1       → user 基本資料
GET /users/1/posts → user 文章
GET /users/1/comments → 留言
```
3 個 round trip、且回多餘資料（你只要名字、卻收到全部）。

## GraphQL 解
```graphql
query {
  user(id: 1) {
    name
    posts(limit: 5) { title }
    comments { content }
  }
}
```
1 個 request、只拿要的。

## Schema 設計

```graphql
type Query {
  user(id: ID!): User
  posts(limit: Int = 10, offset: Int = 0): [Post!]!
  searchPosts(query: String!): [Post!]!
}

type Mutation {
  createPost(input: CreatePostInput!): Post!
  deletePost(id: ID!): Boolean!
}

type User {
  id: ID!
  email: String!
  name: String!
  posts: [Post!]!
}

type Post {
  id: ID!
  title: String!
  content: String!
  author: User!
  createdAt: DateTime!
}

input CreatePostInput {
  title: String!
  content: String!
}

scalar DateTime
```

## Resolver
```typescript
const resolvers = {
  Query: {
    user: async (_, { id }) => db.user.findUnique({ where: { id } })
  },
  User: {
    posts: async (parent) => db.post.findMany({ where: { authorId: parent.id } })
  }
};
```

## N+1 問題 + DataLoader
```typescript
const userLoader = new DataLoader(async (ids) => {
  const users = await db.user.findMany({ where: { id: { in: ids } } });
  return ids.map(id => users.find(u => u.id === id));
});

const resolvers = {
  Post: {
    author: (parent) => userLoader.load(parent.authorId)
  }
};
```

10 個 post → 10 次 author query → 1 次 batch query。

## 框架

### Apollo Server
最熱門：
```typescript
import { ApolloServer } from "@apollo/server";
const server = new ApolloServer({ typeDefs, resolvers });
```

### GraphQL Yoga
輕量、modern。

### Pothos
TypeScript-first、code-first。

### Hasura / Postgraphile
自動從 PG schema 產 GraphQL。

## REST vs GraphQL

| | REST | GraphQL |
|---|---|---|
| 學習 | 平 | 中 |
| 上手 | 快 | 慢 |
| Over-fetch | 有 | 無 |
| Cache | 好（HTTP）| 難 |
| 工具 | 多 | 多 |
| Mobile 友善 | 中 | 高 |

## 心法
- REST 90% 場景夠
- GraphQL 適合 mobile + 複雜 relation
- 別新人專案用 GraphQL（複雜度）
- tRPC 是 TS 全棧的折衷

